<h2>Prerequisites</h2>
<p class="{data:php_version}"><strong>PHP:</strong> Version 5.3 or greater is required</p>
<p class="{data:file_permissions}"><strong>Writable:</strong> Twist folder and subfolders must be writable</p>
<p class="{data:php_curl}"><strong>cURL:</strong> PHP cURL must be installed to use one-click updates</p>
<p class="{data:php_mysql}"><strong>MySQL:</strong> PHP MySQL or MySQLi must be installed to enable all features</p>
<p class="{data:php_zip}"><strong>Zip:</strong> PHP Zip must be installed to enable updates and installations</p>
<p class="{data:php_cookies}"><strong>Cookies:</strong> You must have cookies enabled to login to the framework manager</p>
